Package: BRASSVis
Title: Visualization of Structural Variants from BRASS
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Bartosz", "Czech", email = "bartosz.w.czech@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9908-3007"))
Description: Visualize gene fusions and structural variants detected by
    BRASS (BReakpoint AnalySiS) from whole-genome sequencing data. Reads
    BEDPE files and produces publication-ready PDF reports showing
    breakpoints, exon structure, ideograms, circos plots, and protein
    domain retention. Based on the Arriba visualization approach adapted
    for WGS structural variant data.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/bczech/BRASSVis
BugReports: https://github.com/bczech/BRASSVis/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
